sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>TrafficFilterPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>TrafficFilterRuleListCreateView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>TrafficFilterRuleToggleView
    participant SER as TrafficFilterRuleSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Navigate to Traffic Filters page
    FE->>API1: GET /api/traffic-filters/
    API1->>DB: TrafficFilterRule.objects.filter(environment=env)
    DB-->>API1: QuerySet[TrafficFilterRule]
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {rules: [...]}
    FE-->>U: Display filter rules table
    U->>FE: Fill new rule form (type, pattern, action)
    FE->>API1: POST /api/traffic-filters/ {filter_type: "ip_range", pattern, action: "auto_block"}
    API1->>SER: TrafficFilterRuleSerializer.validate(data)
    API1->>DB: TrafficFilterRule.objects.create(...)
    DB-->>API1: Rule created
    API1-->>FE: 201 Created {rule}
    FE-->>U: New rule added to table
    U->>FE: Toggle rule on/off
    FE->>API2: POST /api/traffic-filters/{id}/toggle/
    API2->>DB: rule.is_active = not rule.is_active
    API2->>DB: rule.save()
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK {is_active: false}
    FE-->>U: Rule toggle updated
